# Changelog

All notable changes to OpenMM MD Runner will be documented in this file.

## [1.0.0] - 2025-01-15

### ðŸŽ‰ Initial Release

#### Added
- Interactive mode with step-by-step guided setup
- Configuration file support (YAML/JSON)
- Checkpoint and restart capability
- Comprehensive analysis module with 9+ plot types
- H-bond analysis across trajectory
- Energy conservation tracking (drift analysis)
- Automatic HTML report generation
- Batch mode for automation
- Analysis-only mode for post-processing

#### Features
- Energy minimization
- NVT equilibration with temperature control
- NPT production runs with pressure control
- Multiple force field presets (AMBER, CHARMM)
- Automatic solvation with padding or manual box
- PME electrostatics
- HBond constraints for efficiency
- Multi-platform support (CPU/CUDA/OpenCL)

#### Analysis Plots
1. Energy components (Potential, Kinetic, Total)
2. Energy with temperature (dual Y-axis)
3. Relative energy drift
4. Cumulative standard deviation
5. Energy fluctuations
6. Density and volume evolution
7. Temperature distribution
8. Equilibration summary
9. Combined simulation timeline
10. Hydrogen bond analysis

#### Documentation
- Comprehensive README with examples
- Inline code documentation
- Usage examples
- Troubleshooting guide
